                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Her face was in a bed of hair,</l>
                    <l>Like flowers in a plot -</l>
                    <l>Her hand was whiter than the sperm</l>
                    <l>That feeds the sacred light.</l>
                    <l>Her tongue more<add type="alternate" extent="tender">timid &amp;#x2022; magic</add>
 tender than the<add type="alternate" extent="tune">tone</add>
 tune</l>
                    <l>That totters in the leaves -</l>
                    <l>Who hears may be incredulous,</l>
                    <l>Who witnesses, believes.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
